1. Danas ću *uložiti* novac na nekoliko konjskih trka. (Today, I will *bet* money on several horse races.)
2. Kladionice su prepune ljudi koji vole da *klade* novac na sportske događaje. (The betting shops are full of people who like to *bet* money on sports events.)
3. On je već *opkladio* sve svoje novce na ovu utakmicu. (He has already *bet* all his money on this game.)
4. Šta misliš, koliko će *oklada* biti na ovu utakmicu? (What do you think, how much will the *betting* be on this game?)
5. Oni su *pobjedili* na kladionici i osvojili veliki novac. (They *won* at the betting shop and won a lot of money.)
6. Moramo *isplatiti* dobitak ovom čovjeku koji je dobio našu opkladu. (We have to *pay out* the winnings to this man who won our bet.)
7. Koliko si *dobro* upoznat sa pravilima sportskog klađenja? (How *well* do you know the rules of sports betting?)
8. Njihov posao je *primati* oklade i brinuti se da se sve odvija po pravilima. (Their job is to *accept* bets and make sure everything is done according to the rules.)
9. Nemoj *kockati* svoj novac, to je loša navika. (Don't *gamble* your money, it's a bad habit.)
10. On je *opkladio* svoj auto da će njegova omiljena ekipa pobijediti. (He *bet* his car that his favorite team will win.)